</comment>
                    <comment id="12464735" author="dpfister" created="Mon, 15 Jan 2007 10:36:43 +0000"  >Added a flag to jackrabbit&amp;#39;s Event implementation, indicating whether it originates from another node in the cluster. SearchManager checks the origin of an event before complaining about unfound, newly created items.&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;br/&gt;
Fixed in revision 496271.</comment>
